Summary: Simple Post-Quantum Signature library
Home-page: https://github.com/pibara/pyspqsigs
Author: Rob J Meijer
Author-email: pibara@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: Library for hash-based signatures using BLAKE2, salt, double WOTS chains, and Merkle-trees.
        
            Development of this library has been discontinued in favor of work on the new coinZdense project.
        
            See https://coin.z-den.se/ for more info.
        
            
